title: MBMBaM 507: Dirtiest Dancing: Havana Nights
description:
If we’re gonna make it through this things, we’re gonna have to find genuine soul connections using Digital. And sometimes, we find Digital in the strangest of places, when we’re least expecting it.
 

Suggested talking point: An Important Digital Communication, Delivery Heroism, Prankin’ Apple, Tooth Fairy Substitutions, Extremely Dirty Dancing, Mystery Squirt
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Justin McElroy, Griffin McElroy, Travis McElroy)
